    <h4>What are the rules?</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>You cannot win or lose anything here. This is only for fun.</li>
        <li>You may only make bets for a whole match, not only for a half.</li>
        <li>You can make bets for every match that is not started already.</li>
        <li>No one, except you, will see your bet until the match starts.</li>
        <li>You get points if you made a bet for a match and the match is over.</li>
        <li>You win the game if you are rank 1 on the highscore list after the final match.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>How do I score?</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>You get {{> correct_bet}} for a correct bet OR</li>
        <li>You get {{> correct_diff}} for the correct goal difference OR</li>
        <li>You get {{> correct_winner}} for the correct winner OR</li>
        <li>You get zero points in any other case or if you did not make a bet</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Scoring Example</h4>
    <p>You made this bet: 4:3 in the match Germany - Denmark. You would get</p>
    <ul>
        <li>{{> correct_bet}}, if the result was 4:3</li>
        <li>{{> correct_diff}}, if the result was 1:0, 2:1 or 3:2 ...</li>
        <li>{{> correct_winner}}, if the winner was Germany</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You made this bet: 2:2 in another match. You would get</p>
    <ul>
        <li>{{> correct_bet}}, if the result was 2:2</li>
        <li>{{> correct_diff}}, if the result was 0:0, 1:1, 3:3 ...</li>
    </ul>

